         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[Dr Mueller wrote to me at the end of October that he was about to embark on a new journey to the mountains. ¶ ]...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">54.10.00b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Wilhelm Sonder</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found. The text given here is extracted from the image of Brief 25 in Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), pp.145-6, W. Sonder to D. von Schlechtendal, 1 January 1855. Among other things, Sonder's letter discusses the progress of Plantae Muellerianae, especially a new consignment of mosses that he hopes Hampe and Carl Müller will again deal with; done in Hampe (1856).</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-size: 13pt; ">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Sonder also requested a catalogue from an antiquarian bookseller as 'ich soll für Dr. Müller verschiedene auf die Flora Australiens bezügliche Werke besorgen" <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[I am supposed to procure for Dr Mueller various works relating to the flora of Australia].</p>
               </note>[Dr. Müller schrieb mir Ende Oktober, dass er im Begriffe sei, eine neue Reise in die Gebirge anzutreten.]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">[Dr Mueller wrote to me at the end of October that he was about to embark on a new journey to the mountains.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M departed on his new expedition on 1 November 1854; see M to J. Foster, 31 October 1854.</p>
               </note>]</p>
         </div>
      </body>
